{"tid":1061434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"78歲阿嬤被劫色　吃了老衲的降魔杵還被說「謝謝」","createTime":"2019-03-14T11:38:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T12:13:23.000Z","uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ffec5228793efb0f7dd718e9f51b2ff2b718c72d","tid":1061434,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T11:38:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xJ9oJ5Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxJ9oJ5Z.png&h=15b375a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰國一名40多歲的和尚持刀劫色，跟78歲阿嬤啪啪啪後還跟她說了聲「謝謝」才逃跑。<br />\n <br />\n據泰國《Thairath》報導，甲米府空統縣一名78歲阿嬤13日報案，稱她被當地寺廟的40多歲和尚性侵，結束後該名和尚還厚臉皮跟她道謝後才逃跑。事發後，阿嬤也立即去醫院驗傷，警方接獲通報後也趕到阿嬤說的寺廟調查，不過進去後只看到地板上掉了個枕頭，並未發現該名和尚。<br />\n <br />\n這名阿嬤說，她跟丈夫住在一起，事發當天她去寺廟旁採腰果，結果和尚就持刀朝她走來，挾持後在禪房隔間性侵，和尚噴發後還跟她說「謝謝」才逃跑。警方調查，該和尚才搬來10天左右，不知道他的名字，之後會詢問相關人員來調查。"},{"pid":"fa208a57b39ab1971e4ca3a23acec7d23dfbedc6","tid":1061434,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T11:40:11.000Z","msg":"無圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5806835b56012ba7b8c5f89a426c664f482414c","tid":1061434,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T11:41:46.000Z","msg":"召喚老衲"},{"pid":"43370fa869770c54e34ee2939aaa41a0030dc6d1","tid":1061434,"uid":116330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T11:43:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe62cc4053cc58eee879fb388727f5507fc4d21","tid":1061434,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T11:43:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201501/f0886a5ad51203577c707fc39e9c7aeb.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201501%2Ff0886a5ad51203577c707fc39e9c7aeb.JPG&h=273b5d85&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f7aabdef1950f21cfd2627b1d3f5e03f1090bb5","tid":1061434,"uid":110508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T11:47:40.000Z","msg":"棋靈王出家？"},{"pid":"48e7ac4ffbba43996619a236abf983cec8f111cd","tid":1061434,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efe62cc4053cc58eee879fb388727f5507fc4d21","tid":1061434,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T11:43:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201501/f0886a5ad51203577c707fc39e9c7aeb.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201501%2Ff0886a5ad51203577c707fc39e9c7aeb.JPG&h=273b5d85&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T12:13:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}